        "created_at": "2020-01-12T22:19:07.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p><a href=\"https://www.cellartracker.com/note.asp?iWine=3258341&amp;iNote=8119971\"><strong>2017 Domaine Pattes Loup Chablis Vent d\u2019Ange</strong></a> <em>- France, Burgundy, Chablis (1/12/2020)</em><br>\nThis smells exactly like a fresh cut lemon. It tastes like dry lemonade made with mineral water. The fresh lemon persists on the finish, nearly to the point of being mouth puckering. Interesting stuff.</p>\n<p><em>Posted from <a href=\"https://www.cellartracker.com/\">CellarTracker</a></em></p>",
