        "created_at": "2020-01-12T22:33:06.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I bought a fair bit of Pattes Loup in the late noughties. Can\u2019t remember exact vintage. They were lean and very tasty on release, but they did not last. Advanced quite rapidly. Drink them young, but gotta love '17 vintage Chablis.</p>",
