        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.wineberserkers.com/dennis_atick/{size}/429_2.png",
        "created_at": "2020-01-13T00:59:32.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I love the '14 Pattes Loup wines. Butteaux, Beuaregard, and Vallions have been very strong for me thus far.</p>",
